    "description": "Tournament Tower is a deckbuilding roguelike game where card battles meet rock-paper-scissors. <br><br>Take part in a never-ending wacky martial arts tournament, set in a world inspired by classic shonen and fighting games, animated frame by frame with a 2010s stylized approach and a bit of western influences.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/cc30cc9768034013d0decf5031edbd66.webp?t=1697796206\" width=600 height=35 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/edfaf3ba1404d13b1a6ee5a1591c0942.poster.avif?t=1697796206\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/edfaf3ba1404d13b1a6ee5a1591c0942.webm?t=1697796206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/edfaf3ba1404d13b1a6ee5a1591c0942.mp4?t=1697796206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each card represents a move that belongs to one of three types: Rock, Paper and Scissors. Your move and your opponent’s move are always played at the same time, and the outcome of the round determines both damage dealt and card effects.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/cffe7cfabc2d12cdf9837dcd158ecfd9.poster.avif?t=1697796206\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/cffe7cfabc2d12cdf9837dcd158ecfd9.webm?t=1697796206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br>Face a varied cast of enemies, each one with a different set of moves and behavioral patterns: pay attention to their hints and try to form a strategy, while constantly balancing out risk and reward.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/1781ee6557f5d98eadcff5944827e694.webp?t=1697796206\" width=600 height=35 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/538d92d7d7e9e15978ed7e97e68cf833.poster.avif?t=1697796206\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/538d92d7d7e9e15978ed7e97e68cf833.webm?t=1697796206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/538d92d7d7e9e15978ed7e97e68cf833.mp4?t=1697796206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Add new moves to your deck between each battle, remove the ones you don’t want, while also getting stronger yourself with stat upgrades and passive times.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/a749589c7ecd5f975aa7cc85ea23fbb3.poster.avif?t=1697796206\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/a749589c7ecd5f975aa7cc85ea23fbb3.webm?t=1697796206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/a749589c7ecd5f975aa7cc85ea23fbb3.mp4?t=1697796206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Each time you get defeated you will have to start a new run, but all of the knowledge you acquired along the way will help you get higher each time. Try and try again, get stronger and climb to the top!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/4c19bce791c670a551d1eba0118a0427.poster.avif?t=1697796206\" width=600 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/4c19bce791c670a551d1eba0118a0427.webm?t=1697796206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
